  <brief_title>The Preventive Effect of Helicobacter Pylori Eradication on the Development of Gastric Cancer</brief_title>
  <official_title>The Effect of Helicobacter Pylori Eradication on the Development of Gastric Cancer and the Medical Care Cost in Iijima Town</official_title>
  <sponsors>
